<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
  <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <hr>
    <p>In 2017 I moved from Vancouver Canada to Saitama Japan and started teaching
       English. I also discovered <a href="https://www.theodinproject.com/" target="_blank">
       The Odin Project</a>.</p>
    <p>This blog is my way of sharing what I have learned as I work through the
       Odin curriculum, meet other developers, and build stuff.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
    <h2>Stuff I've Written</h2>
    <hr>

    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b, %d") %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-3 homepage_content">
    <h2>Stuff I've Built</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b, %d") %></p>
    <% end %>

  </div>
</div>
